    16 NUnit tests under VTuberSystemBase.CoreIpc.Tests.Editor that exercise
    every contract called out in tasks.md §2.1: round-trip parity for state /
    event / request / response (incl. correlationId preservation), explicit
    wire-format assertions (camelCase fields, lowercase "kind"), unknown-field
    forward compatibility (Req 3.7), 1 MB size-limit enforcement on Decode
    plus a boundary check that an in-budget envelope decodes, major-version
    mismatch rejection for both 2.x and 3.x payloads, malformed JSON =>
    InvalidEnvelope, missing protocolVersion / unknown kind value =>
    InvalidEnvelope, null protocolVersion on Encode => InvalidEnvelope, null
    options rejected by the constructor, and default(JsonElement) payload
    serialized as JSON null. Helper AssertEnvelopeEqual compares all fields
    incl. payload via JsonElement.GetRawText().
